#. type: Content of: <dedication><title>
#: lfs-en/prologue/dedication.xml
msgid "Dedication"
msgstr "献词"

#. type: Content of: <dedication><para>
#: lfs-en/prologue/dedication.xml
msgid "This book is dedicated to Ken Moffat."
msgstr "献给 Ken Moffat。"

#. type: Content of: <dedication><para>
#: lfs-en/prologue/dedication.xml
msgid ""
"Ken Moffat first posted to the LFS mailing lists on May 19th, 2001.  There "
"he discussed building LFS from the previous February.  In the last 25 years "
"Ken became an editor and active on the mailing lists, always willing to help."
msgstr ""
"2001 年 5 月 19 日，Ken Moffat 首次通过 LFS 邮件列表发文，提到他自 2000 年 2 "
"月开始构建 LFS。在过去的 25 年中，Ken 成为了一位 LFS 编辑，总是热心地通过邮件"
"列表提供帮助。"

#. type: Content of: <dedication><para>
#: lfs-en/prologue/dedication.xml
msgid ""
"One of Ken's avid interests was computer fonts.  To that end he created a "
"website that is still active at <ulink url=\"https://"
"typosetting.linuxfromscratch.org/\"/>.  He was also the editor who "
"spearheaded the security advisories and he took care of countless security "
"updates and problems during his time as an editor."
msgstr ""
"Ken 热爱计算机字体。为此，他创立了 <ulink url=\"https://"
"typosetting.linuxfromscratch.org/\"/> 这一仍然可用的网站。他也是 LFS 安全公告"
"的先驱者，在他担任 LFS 编辑时，处理了大量的安全问题和安全更新。"

#. type: Content of: <dedication><para>
#: lfs-en/prologue/dedication.xml
msgid "Ken passed away on June 26th, 2025.  He is missed."
msgstr "Ken 逝于 2025 年 6 月 26 日。我们会永远怀念他。"
